item.description:
wget -qO - https://codeberg.org/vhs/after-dark/raw/branch/trunk/bin/install | sh  Run the above command in a terminal emulator after installing Hugo to start a new website in 5-10 seconds. Hugo version 0.51 or greater required.
 After Dark includes a portable installation script for quick set-up. Please install Hugo 0.51 or greater before running:
